Class MyStack<Item>

  • java.lang.Object
    • mazesolver.data_structures.MyStack<Item>
  • Type Parameters:
    Item - Defines the type of items stored in the stack.

    public class MyStack<Item>
extends Object
    Provides implementation for a "first in first out" type datastructure using generic arrays. The array grows automatically if limit is reached.
    Author:
    Marko Vainio
